description:
Merchants that sell new and used automotive, aircraft, and farm
vehicles, parts, equipment, and supplies not elsewhere classified.
Vehicles for sale may include all-terrain vehicles (ATVs), dune buggies,
golf carts, go-carts, snowmobiles, tractors, combines, and harvesting
machinery.
